current.benefit:
During the Surprise Round, if you damage a Flat-Footed target, that target is also knocked Prone if your attack roll also exceeds the target's Fortitude Defense. The target adds its size modifier to its Fortitude Defense:

- Colossal, +50;
- Gargantuan, +20;
- Huge, +10;
- Large, +5;
- Medium and smaller, +0.
